      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，是用packet-beta格式来画。我先确认一下层级：Frame Control字段对应GradeSync，Duration/ID对应ClassroomService，这样理解对吗？另外Address字段有三到四个，需要分别绑定不同的教育服务模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frame Control",
        "Duration/ID",
        "Address 1",
        "Address 2",
        "Address 3",
        "Address 4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。Address 1作为Receiver接收端，绑定StudentDB，因为学生数据库是请求的最终目的地。Address 2作为Transmitter发射端，给ContentCDN，内容从这里发出。Address 3做BSSID和Filter过滤功能，也归StudentDB管，保证数据只流向授权的学生群体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Address 1 - Receiver",
        "Address 2 - Transmitter",
        "Address 3 - BSSID/Filter",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础字段画出来：0-15位是Frame Control标注GradeSync，16-31位Duration/ID标注ClassroomService，32-79位Address 1绑定StudentDB作为Receiver，80-127位Address 2绑定ContentCDN作为Transmitter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Frame Control (Education_GradeSync)",
        "Duration/ID (Education_ClassroomService)",
        "Address 1 - Receiver (Education_StudentDB)",
        "Address 2 - Transmitter (Education_ContentCDN)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来处理Sequence Control和Address 4。Sequence Control给LMS Portal，因为学习管理平台需要维护课程内容的传输顺序。Address 4是可选字段，也分配给LMS Portal，用于跨网段漫游时的额外寻址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequence Control",
        "Address 4",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Sequence Control放在176-191位，Address 4放在192-239位，都标注LMS Portal，并且注明Optional。这样Address 3的BSSID/Filter还是保持StudentDB对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequence Control (Education_LMS_Portal)",
        "Address 4 (Education_LMS_Portal) - Optional",
        "Address 3 - BSSID/Filter (Education_StudentDB)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。然后QoS Control和HT Control这两个可选字段都给ContentCDN，内容分发对服务质量和高吞吐量有强需求。Data Payload部分暂时留空，后面再补具体的教育数据类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QoS Control",
        "HT Control",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Data Payload"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：240-255位QoS Control标注ContentCDN Optional，256-287位HT Control同样标注ContentCDN Optional，288-319位Data Payload先留白。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QoS Control (Education_ContentCDN) - Optional",
        "HT Control (Education_ContentCDN) - Optional",
        "Data Payload"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Data Payload后面我想加一个字段，专门标注StudentDB，表示实际承载的学生数据实体。然后是标准的Frame Check Sequence，最后FCS-CRC部分回归GradeSync，形成闭环——成绩同步系统负责最终的数据完整性校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
