    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了：320-335位标注StudentDB，336-367位是Frame Check Sequence，368-383位FCS-CRC标注GradeSync。整个帧结构从控制到数据到校验，教育服务模块的映射都完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
