      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终确认所有字段：0-15 Frame Control GradeSync，16-31 Duration/ID ClassroomService，32-79 Address 1 StudentDB，80-127 Address 2 ContentCDN，128-175 Address 3 StudentDB，176-191 Sequence LMS，192-239 Address 4 LMS Optional，240-255 QoS ContentCDN Optional，256-287 HT ContentCDN Optional，288-319 Data Payload，320-335 StudentDB，336-367 FCS，368-383 FCS-CRC GradeSync。",
